            "description": "Humans have always been obsessed and interested in flying \ud83d\ude80. Numerous successful and unsuccessful experiments \ud83d\udca5 have been undertaken to make this possible. We always want more and nowadays flying has been taking to new heights \ud83d\udcc8 . \n\nDrones are unmanned objects in the air \ud83e\udd16 . They are revolutionizing economic sectors from Agriculture to Transport\u26a1\ufe0f. Drone\u2019s make impractical routes practical, open up new perspectives, are speedy and faster \ud83d\udd52 .\n\nIngredients of the projects and for our Techie\u2019s \ud83e\udd18 : Tello Drone, GitHub Project DJITelloPy to connect \ud83d\udcbb , OpenCV, Neural Network learning algorithm backpropagation \u201cAdaboost\u201d to detect faces and upper bodys \ud83d\ude0a , YouTube channel of CV ZONE \ud83d\udc4c and a lot fine tuning of the velocity, rotation, in-depth calculations \u270d\ufe0f . Real-world projects requiring Teamwork \ud83d\udc46 .",
